{"type": "article", "id": 9316, "title": "Google 无人驾驶汽车，如何理解骑手的手势", "description": "计算机用曲折的方式感知世界。", "date": "2015-05-08T08:27:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 2489, "name": "无人驾驶汽车"}, {"id": 9834, "name": "自行车手势"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}], "category": 4, "column": null, "author": 3630, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604222637tXhnK7kegJL04QiG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">去年 4 月，Google 宣布无人驾驶汽车能识别自行车手的手势动作了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">最近关于自行车手的手势识别<a href=\"http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&amp;Sect2=HITOFF&amp;d=PALL&amp;p=1&amp;u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsrchnum.htm&amp;r=1&amp;f=G&amp;l=50&amp;s1=9014905.PN.&amp;OS=PN/9014905&amp;RS=PN/9014905\" target=\"_blank\">专利公布</a>了，我们来看看 Google 是怎么做到的吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">在硬件上，Google 无人驾驶汽车使用了摄像机、激光雷达和普通雷达来收集信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">摄像机能得到视频和图像，雷达传递距离信息，这样就得到了有 3 维坐标的图像信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">然后 Google 基于这些图像，采用计算机视觉匹配、机器学习等方法进行分析。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">首先从整体判断视野中是否出现骑行的人。Google 的图像识别技术能把脑袋和路面识别出来，然后计算脑袋顶部和路面的距离。通过把它和一般骑手的高度范围进行匹配，以及骑手身处路的位置和速度信息，以此确定视野中的物体是否是骑行的人。另外，当骑手在等红绿倾斜着地的时候，Google 也能识别出来。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">确定对象后，Google 会找到骑手的身体、头部、胳膊和手，然后把骑手的手势和骑行通用规则进行比较。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222637UqGVmksJAtbo5WPl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Google 会计算车手头部和手的距离。距离小多半意味着拐弯，距离长意味着减速或停止。Google 也会考虑车手手肘的弯曲角度、手型、胳膊和头部的形状大小。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">除了自行车外，Google 表示下一步是识别脚踏车、摩托车等出行设备。它们一般不会有汽车的左拐、右拐和减速的灯光提示，所以需要其他方法来获取行驶信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t题图来自：<a href=\"http://abcnews.go.com/International/auto-revolution-promising-future-driving-cars/story?id=18378323\" target=\"_blank\">abcnews</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}